{"tid":206390,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"［A/I] 遊戲王 Duel Links [17] 又柏加索斯","createTime":"2017-04-18T10:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T07:45:33.000Z","uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e320b5b0b5d135fcf1758afb4ba194426c69b93","tid":206390,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">洗唔洗刷首抽</span><br />\n唔洗，個box啲卡限死數量，終有一日會抽晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解個場得三格/點解deck限20-30張卡</span><br />\n本遊戲採取快速決鬥規則<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點拎角色</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.isheart.com/archives/4433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.isheart.com%2Farchives%2F4433&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1098f124\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.isheart.com/archives/4433</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">啲卡點拎</span><br />\n分別有<br />\n角色等級獎勵<br />\n卡片商人 (stage7 unlock)<br />\n路人掉落<br />\n打Gate<br />\n同埋抽卡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫Reset 卡包</span><br />\n卡包入面嘅卡有限，想得到更多限量卡就要用reset去重置<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新手抽邊個卡包好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n流星黑龍包&gt;暴君龍包&gt;天使包&gt;鳥獸包&gt;混沌士兵包<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點set技能</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/13/110027_99ac597844832fc8b37f05deb821e538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F13%2F110027_99ac597844832fc8b37f05deb821e538.jpg&h=325aa7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Quiz點打</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=29618&amp;snB=318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D29618%26snB%3D318&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c6d427f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/Co.php?bsn=29618&amp;snB=318</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">打Gate有咩要注意</span><br />\n除左解任之外儲key先<br />\n等到unlock lv40先去刷卡刷技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結算分點計</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u2dtrpnz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu2dtrpnz&h=6c55a497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點樣刷到高分</span><br />\n魔導獸deck<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=J5cN0TBKmWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshared%3Fci%3DJ5cN0TBKmWE&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c58251e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=J5cN0TBKmWE</a><br />\n打法係堆攻擊力過一萬同壓血<br />\n（其實一隻魔導獸都得）<br />\n*<span style=\"color: gold;\">只刷到部分角色</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫派小智/流浪者/神秘人/紅帽 etc</span><br />\n係你加左好友之後<br />\n有時打完佢會問你有冇朋友介紹，同埋要set咩challenge 俾佢<br />\n揀一張卡起手就啱架啦，超過二千經驗值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">免費石呀！！！</span></span><br />\n點觸遊戲介面以下地方可獲得數量1、3、5顆不等的石頭。<br />\n1.噴水池：出現噴水彩虹<br />\n2.街燈：發出彩虹光<br />\n3.商店上方卡片：出現禮物汽球<br />\n4.垃圾桶：出現強慾之壺<br />\n獲得一定時間過後可再次點觸獲得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Duellinks卡表網</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.korekara.url.tw/yogioh/deck/deck.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.korekara.url.tw%2Fyogioh%2Fdeck%2Fdeck.html&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8c6eff0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.korekara.url.tw/yogioh/deck/deck.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參考兼攻略網</span><br />\n英文<a href=\"http://duellinks.gamea.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fduellinks.gamea.co%2F&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=67696ce9\" target=\"_blank\">http://duellinks.gamea.co/</a><br />\n日文<a href=\"https://duellinks.gamewith.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fduellinks.gamewith.jp%2F&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=cd7d926f\" target=\"_blank\">https://duellinks.gamewith.jp/</a>"},{"pid":"c9f135ad58e36a8319741888812a231f747c14f3","tid":206390,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"有人問點解鳥獸包排咁後<br />\n因為冇場地成包就廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手唔會咁快刷到技<br />\n不如抽啲百搭卡黎用<br />\n<br />\n如果刷到場 鳥獸包就會優先"},{"pid":"fa08782552048d846e0f7e914aa885310d3503b0","tid":206390,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:48:35.000Z","msg":"[I/A] 遊戲王 Duel Links 1001識開post未<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/205975/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/205975/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4b3dfdedfbaa329f173710cf38eb313276e02518","tid":206390,"uid":96097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:45:33.000Z","msg":"開到未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}